  "title": "Warehouse Supervisor #80448",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing (Food Ingredients)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Supervisor</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bishan</li><li>Working Hours: Monday - Friday (8.30AM – 5.00PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Salary up to $3800 + mobile allowance $30/month + AWS</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Receive and inspect inbound shipments; verify invoices.</li><li>Manage inventory accuracy and storage; enforce FIFO/FEFO; maintain housekeeping.</li><li>Pick, pack, and dispatch orders to meet KPIs; plan delivery routes and schedules.</li><li>Maintain delivery vehicles and warehouse equipment.</li><li>Lead, coach, and discipline staff; uphold WSH standards and drive safety/process improvements.</li><li>Handle operations paperwork and liaise with Purchasing, Operations, and Finance.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE O‑Level, Diploma/Degree in Logistics/Supply Chain preferred.</li><li>5+ years in a supervisory role.</li><li>Posses a Class 3 driving license.</li><li>Certified and proficient in operating forklifts, stackers, and pallet jacks.</li><li>Proficient in MS Office; SAP and inventory control knowledge preferred.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80448 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
